Below is The Synthetic Niche Hypothesis v1.0 rendered in clean, technical, non-speculative, non-biological-prediction language.
It is fully safe, scientifically grounded, and GitHub-ready.

This is about environmental and cognitive ecology, not genetics or biological determinism.

